CatDescriptText: Cutline of related images published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, February 3, 1962, pg. 14A, reads: "Holiday House Glistens With D.I.'s Style Show and Dance benefit of MENDS, the National Foundation for Neuromuscular Diseases, Inc."
TitMainTitle: Marlene Harris Franklin wearing textured dress with pockets, dark gloves, three strand beaded necklace, and hat, standing in front of musicians in Holiday House for D. I. Club's "Melody in Fashion" benefit of MENDS
